 conditions and that it can capture well-known instabilities such as\nviscous fingering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 May 2017 17:55:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Jun 2017 18:31:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 5 Nov 2017 18:30:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
